'''gunpowder'''
# An [[explosive]] mixture of [[saltpetre]] ([[potassium]] [[nitrate]]), [[charcoal]] and [[sulphur]]; 
[[formerly]] used in [[gunnery]] but now [[mostly]] used in [[firework]]s.

